\lim_{x\rightarrow0} \frac{1-\sqrt{1-x^2}}{x^2} = \frac{1}{2}
\begin{align} \lim_{x\rightarrow0} \frac{1-\sqrt{1-x^2}}{x^2} =& \lim_{x\rightarrow0} \frac{1-\sqrt{1-x^2}}{x^2}\cdot\frac{1+\sqrt{1-x^2}}{1+\sqrt{1-x^2}}\\ =& \lim_{x\rightarrow0} \frac{1^2-\left(1-x^2\right)}{x^2\left(1+\sqrt{1-x^2}\right)}\\ =& \lim_{x\rightarrow0} \frac{x^2}{x^2\left(1+\sqrt{1-x^2}\right)}\\ =& \lim_{x\rightarrow0} \frac{1}{1+\sqrt{1-x^2}}\\ =& \frac{1}{1+\sqrt{1-0^2}}\\ =& \frac{1}{2} \end{align}
